.TH wxToggleButton 3 "wx 2.5.4" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
wxToggleButton \- \fIwxToggleButton\fR is a button that stays pressed when clicked by the user.

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
In other words, it is similar to \fIwxCheckBox\fR in functionality but looks like a \fIwxButton\fR.

.PP
Since wxWidgets version 2.9.0 this control emits an update UI event.

.PP
You can see \fIwxToggleButton\fR in action in page_samples_widgets.

.PP
